title: #96: Hemorrhoad Trip (Brent Weinbach)
itunes:title: \Hemorrhoad Trip with Brent Weinbach
description: Brent Weinbach and I took a road trip home from San Francisco to Los Angeles on New Years day. We stopped at all the places we've always wanted to stop and tasted some delicious new foods. It was the best time I've ever had with an extreme sufferer of OCD. So, take a trip with us back to a time of wonder, a time of innocence, come back to January 1, 2013.
